Class LocalSimilarityRegistry

java.lang.Object
  jcolibri.cbrcore.LocalSimilarityRegistry

public class LocalSimilarityRegistry
extends java.lang.Object

Registry of the managers of the package local similarities. It is implemented using the Singleton pattern.

Author:
Antonio A. Sánchez Ruiz-Granados
